{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a7c26aee6","title":"斗争要文明些，坚持文斗，不用武斗","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cfc058f477","index":0,"year":1966,"month":12,"day":27,"articleId":"8a7c26aee6"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3457e40c94","name":"党内资产阶级","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoxuan-jinghuo","name":"毛泽东选集1-7（静火版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"静火","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/maoxuan-jinghuo.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoxuan-jinghuo":{"comments":[{"id":"25196ee713","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"这是毛泽东同志给周恩来同志的一封信和指示。"},{"id":"17bcd2888c","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6","index":1,"part_index":2,"offset":2,"text":"恩来，周恩来，时任国务院总理。"},{"id":"0a85de0a5c","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6","index":2,"part_index":10,"offset":35,"text":"他们，指有可能翻案的走资本主义当权派。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8f3e0798f4","type":"title","text":"斗争要文明些，坚持文斗，不用武斗","index":0,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"17bcd2888c","type":"subtitle","text":"（一）一九六六年十二月二十七日的信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"0a85de0a5c","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"2a466e5572","type":"paragraph","text":"最近，不少来京革命师生和革命群众来信问我，给走资本主义道路的当权派和牛鬼蛇神戴高帽子、打花脸、游街是否算武斗？","index":3,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"549657d1d9","type":"paragraph","text":"我认为：这种作法应该算是武斗的一种形式。这种作法不好。这种作法达不到教育人民的目的。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"e5e4f29765","type":"paragraph","text":"这里我强调一下，在斗争中一定要坚持文斗，不用武斗，因为武斗只能触及人的身体，不能触及人的灵魂。只有坚持文斗，不用武斗，摆事实，讲道理，以理服人，才能斗出水平来，才能真正达到教育人民的目的。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"0bcf1dd1b1","type":"paragraph","text":"应该分析，武斗绝大多数是少数别有用心的资产阶级反动分子挑动起来的，他们有意破坏党的政策，破坏无产阶级文化大革命，降低党的威信。凡是动手打人的，应该依法处之。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"79f4e4c3ce","type":"paragraph","text":"请转告来京革命师生和革命群众。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"f12ff98a35","type":"subtitle","text":"（二）一九六七年二月三日的指示","index":8,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"87cf6d4bdf","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争要文明些，我们是无产阶级专政，要高姿态，要高风格。北京街头上标语水平不高，到处都打倒、砸烂狗头，那有那么多的狗头，都是人头。这样搞群众很难理解。搞喷气式飞机照相片，登报贴在大街上被外国记者搞走了。现在要将斗争水平提高，现在水平太低。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"7b86f59fa9","type":"paragraph","text":"八月初，也没这凶嘛，斗倒斗臭要在政治上斗臭，要对后代进行教育。不然他们将来掌权了，也这样干，这就太简单化了。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"5b567a3d04","type":"paragraph","text":"他们认为这样斗臭了，还有把别人生活上的问题摆出来也叫斗臭了，我看不合适。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"},{"id":"3e05ccfba0","type":"paragraph","text":"主要是政治上斗臭。","index":12,"publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6"}],"page":{"id":"69b4c0950d","publicationId":"maoxuan-jinghuo","articleId":"8a7c26aee6","start":1573,"end":1573}}}},"__N_SSG":true}